    <item>
      <title>法院规定，德国可以将德国选择党视为对民主的威胁进行监控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/germany-can-monitor-afd-as-threat-to-democracy-court-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周一的一项裁决，德国国内情报机构可以继续监控极右翼的德国另类选择党，将其视为涉嫌极端主义的案件，对民主构成潜在威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/germany-can-monitor-afd-as-threat-to-democracy-court-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
